{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-introduction-to-flexbox/introduction-flexbox-lesson-h","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"top-introduction-to-flexbox","challengeType":15,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Bez obzira na pravac koji koristite, morate uzeti u obzir da vaše fleksibilne kontejneri (flex-containers) imaju dve ose: glavnu osu i poprečnu osu. Pravac ovih osa se menja kada se <code>flex-direction</code> promeni. U većini slučajeva, <code>flex-direction: row</code> postavlja glavnu osu horizontalno (od leve ka desnoj), a <code>column</code> postavlja glavnu osu vertikalno (od vrha do dna).</p>\n<p>Drugim rečima, u našem prvom primeru, stavili ste <code>display: flex</code> unutar diva i to je učinilo da su njegovi potomci vertikalni. Ovo je demonstracija <code>flex-direction: row</code>, podrazumevanih podešavanja. Sledeći primer je vrlo sličan. Ako uklonite komentar na liniji koja kaže <code>flex-direction: column</code>, ti divovi će učiniti stvari vertikalnim.</p>\n<iframe allowfullscreen=\"true\" allowpaymentrequest=\"true\" allowtransparency=\"true\" class=\"cp_embed_iframe \" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"400\" width=\"100%\" name=\"cp_embed_1\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://codepen.io/TheOdinProjectExamples/embed/BaZKPdw?height=400&amp;default-tab=html%2Cresult&amp;slug-hash=BaZKPdw&amp;editable=true&amp;user=TheOdinProjectExamples&amp;name=cp_embed_1\" style=\"width: 100%; overflow:hidden; display:block;\" title=\"CodePen Embed\" loading=\"lazy\" id=\"cp_embed_BaZKPdw\"></iframe>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"Odin","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-introduction-to-flexbox/introduction-flexbox-lesson-h"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Koje CSS svojstvo menja smer glavne ose u fleksibilnim kontejnerima kako bi rasporedilo stavke odozgo nadole?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p><code>align-items</code></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><code>flex-flow</code></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><code>flex-direction</code></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><code>justify-content</code></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null}],"solution":3}],"scene":null,"superBlock":"the-odin-project","tests":[],"title":"Uvod u lekciju fleksboksa H","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":null,"videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/the-odin-project/#top-introduction-to-flexbox","dashedName":"introduction-flexbox-lesson-h","certification":"the-odin-project","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"the-odin-project","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"top-introduction-to-flexbox","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-introduction-to-flexbox/introduction-flexbox-lesson-i","prevChallengePath":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-introduction-to-flexbox/introduction-flexbox-lesson-g","id":"6571c34668e4b3b17d3957f9","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":15,"challengeFiles":[]}},"id":"/learn/the-odin-project/top-introduction-to-flexbox/introduction-flexbox-lesson-h"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}